data.description:
Welcome to your private escape in Louisville, a ranch-style haven cradled by five acres of Kentucky's natural
splendor. This home along with the walk-out basement is ready to cater to your family's needs. Revel in the
outdoor serenity on the large covered deck, or indulge in hobbies in the spacious 5-stall barn equipped with a
tack room. With its own stocked pond and an array of fruit trees, this property invites you to partake in its
bounty. Each room within the residence beckons with warmth and potential, crafting the perfect backdrop for
your new life.
